00:54:40,710 --> 00:54:41,430
听到没有
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}to see another day

483
00:54:42,430 --> 00:54:43,660
唐师父 请
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sifu Tang, our business here is done

484
00:55:23,860 --> 00:55:25,260
限你们三天搬离此地
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We want you to be gone in three days

485
00:55:26,600 --> 00:55:29,030
你们这样无法无天 我们要去找钟老爷评评理
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You guys are ruthless. I'll report this to Master Chung

486
00:55:30,140 --> 00:55:31,060
就是要你们去
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's what we want

487
00:55:44,470 --> 00:55:45,100
浩云 你慢点走
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. Please wait

488
00:55:48,510 --> 00:55:49,980
我是故意在这儿等你的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've been waiting for you

489
00:55:51,710 --> 00:55:52,270
什么事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What can I do for you?

490
00:55:54,420 --> 00:55:56,850
我实在不敢相信 你在跟魏家做事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I can't believe you're working for the Ngais now

491
00:55:58,240 --> 00:55:59,840
不错 我是在替他做事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm definitely working for the Ngais

492
00:56:00,510 --> 00:56:01,880
你不要再继续做下去
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You've got to stop.

493
00:56:02,720 --> 00:56:03,370
还要
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I won't

494
00:56:03,880 --> 00:56:07,440
你要是不了解魏苍龙的为人 我可以告诉你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you want to know more about the Ngais, I can tell you

495
00:56:07,890 --> 00:56:09,580
不必
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No need

496
00:56:10,660 --> 00:56:12,820
他是专门跟我们百忍堂为敌的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's the Patience Clan's arch enemy

497
00:56:13,590 --> 00:56:14,890
我无可选择
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've no other choice

498
00:56:18,430 --> 00:56:21,450
最好你不要去惹他
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You shouldn't provoke him in the future

499
00:56:23,290 --> 00:56:26,020
我真是不明白我们之间还有什么仇怨呢
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't understand, I thought we'd settled all our scores

500
00:56:29,570 --> 00:56:31,260
你真的想知道
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you really want to know?

501
00:56:32,240 --> 00:56:33,200
当然啦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Of course

502
00:56:34,170 --> 00:56:36,540
很简单 我师父已经死啦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's simple. My Sifu is dead

503
00:56:37,470 --> 00:56:41,970
你爹虽然断了一条腿 还活着
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and even though your dad has lost a leg, he's still alive

504
00:56:43,910 --> 00:56:44,880
明白了吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get it now?

505
00:56:45,480 --> 00:56:49,310
怪不得你不回唐山 怪不得你要替魏家做事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No wonder you've not gone back to Tang San No wonder you work for the Ngais

506
00:56:50,980 --> 00:56:53,640
我爹跟我们说过很多次 不许我们恨你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My dad always asks us not to hate you

507
00:56:54,550 --> 00:56:56,810
我一直认为 你是光明正大的男子汉
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I thought you were a man of your word

508
00:56:57,920 --> 00:57:00,250
想不到你是 我恨你 恨你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But you're not. I hate you, I hate you

509
00:57:36,280 --> 00:57:37,000
是你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's you.

510
00:57:37,280 --> 00:57:38,240
我恨死你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll kill you

511
00:57:50,280 --> 00:57:51,150
南英青
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop fighting

512
00:57:56,790 --> 00:57:58,050
不要再打了 不要打了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop fighting, stop fighting

513
00:57:59,790 --> 00:58:02,650
不要打了 不要打了 你们不要再打了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop, you two stop fighting

514
00:58:09,730 --> 00:58:10,710
你还不快点走
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Go now

515
00:58:31,970 --> 00:58:35,030
师娘 这是您喜欢吃的果子 这两块衣料是买给你的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Simo, your favourite cake This fabric is for you

516
00:58:37,040 --> 00:58:38,480
这个颜色我喜欢
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I like the colour. It's nice

517
00:58:39,350 --> 00:58:40,640
师娘 您的药
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Simo, more medicine

518
00:58:40,880 --> 00:58:43,440
正好 药昨天我刚刚吃完了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've just finished mine as well

519
00:58:44,020 --> 00:58:46,680
吃完了 上次给的一百粒没有几天吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's quick, I gave you a hundred tablets last time

520
00:58:47,020 --> 00:58:52,350
我也不知道 以前每次吃三颗就不痛了 现在啊 吃六颗都止不住
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've increased the dosage from three to six tablets to relieve the pain

521
00:58:52,830 --> 00:58:53,940
妈 你怎么没告诉我
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mum, why didn't you tell me?

522
00:58:55,550 --> 00:58:58,380
我的病 已经把你们都烦死了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My illness has troubled you two enough So what if I need to take more medicine?

523
00:58:58,820 --> 00:59:03,420
说来干什么 多吃就多吃点 好啦 只要不痛就是了嘛
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}As long as I'm not in pain. There's no reason to tell you

524
00:59:05,830 --> 00:59:09,390
越吃越多 这也不是个办法啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Having to increase your dosage that's not an ideal solution

525
00:59:11,100 --> 00:59:13,930
浩云 魏财主真是个好人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. Ngai is really a good guy

526
00:59:14,670 --> 00:59:17,190
可是我常常这样麻烦人家也不是个事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've troubled them long enough

527
00:59:18,070 --> 00:59:22,870
能不能这样 求他把方子给我们 我们自己去配就好了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why don't we ask them for the recipe and make the medicine when we're back home?

528
00:59:24,770 --> 00:59:28,230
我每次问他拿这个药都不容易 秘方他不肯给
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's refused me a number of times I don't understand why?

529
00:59:29,080 --> 00:59:33,840
那怎么办呢 为了这个病 我们几时才能回唐山了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What can we do? My illness has kept us here When can we return to Tang San?

530
00:59:34,780 --> 00:59:38,340
师娘 您放心 我在帮他们做事 药他一定会给我的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't worry, Simo I'm working for them now, we'll have no problem getting the medicine

531
00:59:38,920 --> 00:59:40,650
我总会想办法尽快回唐山的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll think of a way to get us back to Tang San as soon as possible

532
00:59:43,190 --> 00:59:44,370
我先回房了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll go and rest now.

533
00:59:49,350 --> 00:59:50,380
唐浩云 唐浩云
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tang How Yuen

534
00:59:54,690 --> 00:59:56,060
这么大声叫我 什么事啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You don't need to shout. What is it?

535
00:59:56,390 --> 00:59:57,950
我们大哥找你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Big Bro's looking for you

536
00:59:58,930 --> 00:59:59,490
天都黑了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's late now.

537
01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:01,260
大概有要紧的事情吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's important

538
01:00:02,330 --> 01:00:03,390
这个
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's see...

539
01:00:03,700 --> 01:00:04,430
走啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come on Mum,

540
01:00:05,700 --> 01:00:10,130
妈 你有没有看出来 师哥心里好像有什么话说不出来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}have you noticed? How Yuen seems to be hiding something

541
01:00:12,060 --> 01:00:14,260
自从你爹死了之后 多亏了他
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's been a great help since your dad died

542
01:00:15,000 --> 01:00:18,490
就算我亲生的儿子 也不会待我们这么好的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He treats me better than any son treats their mother

543
01:00:26,210 --> 01:00:26,800
什么事啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What's up?

544
01:00:33,450 --> 01:00:34,600
哥哥 你上哪儿去呀
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Brother, where are you going?

545
01:00:35,440 --> 01:00:36,670
你睡觉 我们就回来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sleep tight, we'll be back soon

546
01:00:45,990 --> 01:00:48,460
我查到了今天魏家走私的地方 我们去抓去
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know where the Ngais are loading their stuff, let's catch them

547
01:00:48,720 --> 01:00:50,160
那还不告诉师父
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's tell Sifu

548
01:00:51,430 --> 01:00:55,800
不用告诉他老人家 又要说忍啊忍啊不许干 我们先干了再说
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If we tell him, he'll ask us to be patient We'll inform him later.

549
01:01:14,510 --> 01:01:15,840
就在前面 小心点
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}This way

550
01:02:05,840 --> 01:02:07,140
快
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hurry up

551
01:02:12,410 --> 01:02:13,390
快
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Quickly!

552
01:02:15,840 --> 01:02:16,530
站住
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't move

553
01:02:20,480 --> 01:02:22,970
你们在干什么 今天 总算给我们抓到了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What are you doing? Finally got caught in the act?

554
01:02:24,350 --> 01:02:27,150
本少爷要干什么就干什么 你管得着吗 上
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll do what I want, it's none of your business

555
01:03:19,650 --> 01:03:20,740
走
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's go

556
01:03:22,790 --> 01:03:23,620
不准走
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's split up

557
01:03:33,220 --> 01:03:34,150
搜
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Search

558
01:03:39,990 --> 01:03:41,480
这么晚了还有什么事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's getting late, what do you want?

559
01:03:42,160 --> 01:03:46,830
今晚上有一批贷要在这儿交 大哥怕有意外所以叫你来看看
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've got a transaction tonight Big Bro wants you here to make sure nothing goes wrong

560
01:03:49,870 --> 01:03:51,770
这是谁家的小孩 睡在这个地方
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's too late for a kid to be lying here

561
01:03:52,870 --> 01:03:53,890
快
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's look there

562
01:03:57,500 --> 01:03:59,330
是小喜子 小喜子
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kiddo, kiddo!

563
01:04:03,010 --> 01:04:03,870
小喜子
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kiddo!

564
01:04:05,370 --> 01:04:07,100
唐浩云
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tang How Yuen. You're despicable

565
01:04:07,580 --> 01:04:10,270
不是人 你是畜生 我们百忍道场跟你有什么仇
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you have against the Patience Clan now?

566
01:04:10,650 --> 01:04:12,010
连个小孩子你都下得了手
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How could you hurt a child?

567
01:04:12,520 --> 01:04:13,780
我
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I...

568
01:04:18,420 --> 01:04:19,110
你听我说
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let me explain.

569
01:04:19,420 --> 01:04:20,280
还有什么说的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What's there to explain?

570
01:04:29,790 --> 01:04:31,690
到了现在你们还要狠
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How dare you?

571
01:04:32,530 --> 01:04:33,860
出来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Get them

572
01:04:40,300 --> 01:04:43,220
两位 我替你们找的坟地不错吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Isn't this a good location to rest in peace?

573
01:04:44,970 --> 01:04:47,830
唐浩云 大哥叫你到这儿来 就是干这件事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tang How Yuen. Big Bro wants you here to do this

574
01:04:48,430 --> 01:04:49,260
把他们两个干掉
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kill them.

575
01:04:50,100 --> 01:04:50,590
我不干
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No way

576
01:04:50,800 --> 01:04:51,430
你不干
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why not?

577
01:04:51,600 --> 01:04:53,260
我唐浩云做事一向光明磊落
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I think it's dishonourable

578
01:04:53,900 --> 01:04:55,770
你不干 是真的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You really won't do it?

579
01:04:57,440 --> 01:04:58,300
来啊 把他们两干掉
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Guys, kill them.

580
01:04:58,570 --> 01:04:59,440
不许动
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop

581
01:05:02,240 --> 01:05:03,180
放他们走
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let them go

582
01:05:05,580 --> 01:05:10,030
他们好不容易才中了我的计 放他们走 大哥怪起来谁负责
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We don't often get a chance like this If we let them go, who will answer to Big Bro?

583
01:05:10,250 --> 01:05:13,730
我负责 谁不怕死尽管动手
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Me, whoever touches them will die at my hands

584
01:05:14,410 --> 01:05:15,400
你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You...

585
01:05:16,750 --> 01:05:17,410
二位请吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You two can go. -

586
01:05:55,780 --> 01:05:57,110
师姐
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Senior, I'm convinced now

587
01:05:58,080 --> 01:06:00,550
对不起 师弟 没有打痛你吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I hope I didn't hurt you

588
01:06:00,910 --> 01:06:01,870
没有
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}No

589
01:06:10,950 --> 01:06:13,710
小喜子 怎么回事 是谁干的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kiddo. What happened? Who did it?

590
01:06:15,190 --> 01:06:16,020
是谁干的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell me

591
01:06:22,930 --> 01:06:23,950
到底是谁干的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tell me who did it.

592
01:06:25,200 --> 01:06:27,280
你说话 你怎么不说话
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why won't you tell me?

593
01:06:34,830 --> 01:06:36,260
我亲眼看见是姓唐的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I saw Tang do it. I saw Tang do it

594
01:06:36,330 --> 01:06:39,230
我亲眼看见姓唐的干的 我为什么打不过他
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I want to take revenge but I can't beat him

595
01:06:39,470 --> 01:06:40,400
我要报这个仇
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm useless.

596
01:06:43,340 --> 01:06:44,810
这是不可能的事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't believe it

597
01:06:47,410 --> 01:06:48,210
真的是他干的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Are you sure it was him?

598
01:06:49,710 --> 01:06:51,290
是啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It was him

599
01:07:03,420 --> 01:07:04,750
爹
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad...

600
01:07:53,680 --> 01:07:54,870
你们想干什么
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you want?

601
01:08:12,490 --> 01:08:14,050
说不说 许胖子躲在什么地方
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Spit it out. Where's Fatty Hui hiding?

602
01:08:16,490 --> 01:08:18,080
我说 我说
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll tell you

603
01:08:25,800 --> 01:08:26,360
咱们一块去的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Listen up, brother.

604
01:08:26,600 --> 01:08:27,070
是吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is it?

605
01:08:30,310 --> 01:08:34,230
我告诉你昨晚上我泡了个妞 那真是棒级了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let me tell you something. I met a beautiful girl last night

606
01:08:34,800 --> 01:08:38,330
看她年龄顶多十八九岁 那脸蛋是细皮白肉的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}While we were haggling over the price, I touched her and she was ecstatic

607
01:09:50,350 --> 01:09:52,340
不要再打了 我们要留个活口
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Stop, keep him for questioning

608
01:09:56,990 --> 01:09:59,220
姓魏的 你回去告诉你们大哥
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Hey, go and tell your Big Bro

609
01:09:59,860 --> 01:10:02,150
我们回去问清楚了 再来找他算账
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}we'll come for him after we question this one

610
01:10:08,130 --> 01:10:10,360
好 现在是算账的时候了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now is the time to get even

611
01:10:11,500 --> 01:10:14,860
我一直叫大家忍耐 现在忍无可忍
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've always told you guys to be patient but everything has its limit

612
01:10:15,860 --> 01:10:19,130
既然许胖子都招出来了 姓魏的罪大恶极
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Since Fatty Hui's confession. We can confirm that the biggest villain is Ngai

613
01:10:20,000 --> 01:10:21,430
今天我要跟他算清这笔账
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll make sure he pays for it

614
01:10:22,500 --> 01:10:24,530
方刚 拉许胖子出来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Go get Fatty Hui.

615
01:10:24,870 --> 01:10:25,500
是
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes

616
01:10:27,640 --> 01:10:29,160
秋萍 把我的手杖拿来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Chou Ping, get my crutch

617
01:10:29,610 --> 01:10:31,240
爹 你要手杖干什么
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad, what do you need that for?

618
01:10:31,680 --> 01:10:32,970
我要亲自去见姓魏的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I want to go and see Ngai

619
01:10:33,510 --> 01:10:35,640
不好 万一动起手来了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't go. What if he gets physical?

620
01:10:36,650 --> 01:10:38,400
我还有一条腿 去拿啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I still have one leg. Go and get it

621
01:10:40,010 --> 01:10:40,630
哦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}OK, then

622
01:10:49,250 --> 01:10:52,480
许胖子 起来 我们要送你回去了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fatty Hui, get up. We're sending you home now

623
01:10:55,060 --> 01:10:57,180
怎么 你想赖着不走啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What now? Don't want to go?

624
01:11:08,390 --> 01:11:10,860
师父 出了事啦 许胖子被人暗杀了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sifu, bad news. Fatty Hui has been killed

625
01:11:12,900 --> 01:11:15,700
是谁干的 现在连证人都没有了 这怎么办了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Now we've lost our main witness. What shall we do now?

626
01:11:17,940 --> 01:11:19,370
你们说是谁干的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Any idea who did it?

627
01:11:22,570 --> 01:11:23,910
师父 完了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sifu, what shall we do now?

628
01:11:24,680 --> 01:11:27,660
这一次我们跟魏家的账又不能算了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We can't get even with the Ngais now

629
01:11:28,440 --> 01:11:30,460
何止不能算
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's not the worst of it

630
01:11:31,840 --> 01:11:35,440
魏家的人死在我们这儿 他们决不会罢休的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Ngai's man died in our custody. They will hold us responsible

631
01:11:37,050 --> 01:11:39,410
我看很麻烦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We're in real trouble

632
01:11:40,250 --> 01:11:41,650
许胖子死啦 谁说的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Fatty Hui's been killed? Who told you?

633
01:11:41,880 --> 01:11:43,410
小三子亲眼看见的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sun saw it himself

634
01:11:45,520 --> 01:11:48,010
把我的人抓了去随随便便的杀了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They held our man in custody but couldn't even protect him

635
01:11:51,030 --> 01:11:53,950
浩云 你说他们是不是欺人太甚
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. Don't you think they're big bullies?

636
01:11:54,750 --> 01:11:56,810
你别动气 问问清楚再说
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You shouldn't be too upset until you know the truth

637
01:11:57,460 --> 01:12:01,920
现在你没第二条路可走 浩云 我们要他们交出许胖子来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's no other way now. How Yuen. Go and claim Fatty Hui's body

638
01:12:02,730 --> 01:12:06,100
交不出来的话 你替我把百忍道场给拆掉
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Trash Patience Clan's place after that

639
01:12:09,000 --> 01:12:10,590
这件事我绝对不能做
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's something I won't do

640
01:12:11,300 --> 01:12:15,140
你不做 他们认为你杀死小喜子 早晚也不会放过你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You won't do it? They thought you killed Kiddo, they'll come for you next

641
01:12:16,580 --> 01:12:19,470
你在场最清楚了 小喜子不是我杀的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We all know very well that I didn't kill Kiddo

642
01:12:20,540 --> 01:12:22,000
我可以跟他们解释
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You can explain that to them

643
01:12:22,870 --> 01:12:25,200
你用嘴巴说 他们就相信你了吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You think they'll trust what you say?

644
01:12:27,610 --> 01:12:31,550
他们相信不相信都不要紧 这件事我还是不做
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't care but I'll not do it

645
01:12:32,150 --> 01:12:35,380
你想一想 你本来是替师父报仇来的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Think about it, you're working for the Ngais

646
01:12:35,750 --> 01:12:38,690
这是天公地道的 江湖上谁也不能说你不是
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's only right that you protect the Ngai's interests

647
01:12:40,890 --> 01:12:43,870
浩云 我魏苍龙咽不下这口气
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. I won't let this matter rest

648
01:12:44,380 --> 01:12:47,980
你只要替我办妥了这件事 我把秘方送给你 你随时回唐山
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you do this for me, I'll give you the recipe for the medicine You can return to Tang San after that

649
01:12:49,050 --> 01:12:50,150
如果许胖子没有死呢
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What if Fatty Hui's still alive?

650
01:12:50,620 --> 01:12:54,650
那最好了 大家都没事 我药方也一样送给你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's even better. No one loses I'll still give you the recipe

651
01:13:09,580 --> 01:13:10,340
什么事啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Can I help you?

652
01:13:10,520 --> 01:13:11,310
庄小姐住哪间房
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Which room is Lan in?

653
01:13:11,480 --> 01:13:12,810
那间
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That one.

654
01:13:12,920 --> 01:13:13,750
谢谢
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Thank you

655
01:13:24,460 --> 01:13:27,900
我有一点事情 可以跟你谈谈吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've something to talk to you about

656
01:13:34,630 --> 01:13:35,620
庄伯母
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Auntie Zhong.

657
01:13:35,960 --> 01:13:37,860
是你呀 你怎么来了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's you. Can I help?

658
01:13:38,770 --> 01:13:39,730
有什么话你可以说了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you want?

659
01:13:40,770 --> 01:13:43,470
庄姑娘 我可是诚心诚意来的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Lan. I don't have any bad intentions...

660
01:13:44,110 --> 01:13:45,100
谁相信你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Cut the crap

661
01:13:46,740 --> 01:13:48,710
你怎么可以这样讲话呢 请坐
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't be rude. Please be seated

662
01:13:56,950 --> 01:13:57,840
先喝杯热茶
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Have some hot tea.

663
01:14:00,610 --> 01:14:05,240
你们两位可知道 唐浩云在外边做些什么事吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you know what How Yuen's been up to recently?

664
01:14:05,820 --> 01:14:08,250
知道 他在魏财主家里做事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We know. He's doing some manual work for Ngai

665
01:14:09,090 --> 01:14:11,520
不错 可是他做的都是坏事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's definitely working for the Ngais but what he's doing is illegal

666
01:14:12,860 --> 01:14:14,450
坏事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Illegal?

667
01:14:14,860 --> 01:14:16,830
你不要胡说 我师哥不是这种人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Nonsense. How Yuen is not like that The Ngai brothers are the big bullies here

668
01:14:17,860 --> 01:14:22,490
魏家四虎是这里的恶霸 他做了他们的帮凶鱼肉百姓
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen is helping them to oppress the villagers

669
01:14:24,360 --> 01:14:25,660
我真替他不值
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I think he's been misled

670
01:14:26,360 --> 01:14:27,760
我一点都不知道啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I really don't know about this.

671
01:14:28,900 --> 01:14:30,300
不会吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What do you think?

672
01:14:30,600 --> 01:14:31,430
不会
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It can't be

673
01:14:32,230 --> 01:14:36,300
就算我师哥做坏事也与你无关 为什么你要来告诉我们
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Even if it's true, it's none of your business What's your motive for telling us this?

674
01:14:38,870 --> 01:14:41,040
我早就猜到你们两位还不知道
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know you're in the dark about this

675
01:14:41,440 --> 01:14:44,410
所以特地来警告 你们早点回唐山去吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}My advice to you is to return to Tang San quick

676
01:14:46,250 --> 01:14:48,670
我们回不回唐山要听你的吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}When we return to Tang San has nothing to do with you

677
01:14:49,370 --> 01:14:53,470
姓魏的心狠手辣 唐浩云是一个老实人 斗不过他们的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Ngais are too shady for a decent guy like How Yuen They'll exploit him

678
01:14:54,480 --> 01:14:56,110
不要把他的命丢在这儿
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}if he's not careful

679
01:15:04,160 --> 01:15:04,680
再见
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}See you

680
01:15:17,360 --> 01:15:18,830
钟姑娘
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Miss Chung,

681
01:15:20,360 --> 01:15:22,020
我只要跟你说一句话
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've got something to tell you

682
01:15:22,130 --> 01:15:22,830
什么话
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is it?

683
01:15:23,030 --> 01:15:24,830
小喜子的事不是我做的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I didn't kill your brother

684
01:15:58,590 --> 01:16:00,520
你这是干什么 良心惭愧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How could you do it? Haven't you got a conscience?

685
01:16:02,690 --> 01:16:05,650
你在外面做的坏事我全都知道 我去告诉娘去
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I know you've been involved in illegal activities I'll tell Mum.

686
01:16:06,190 --> 01:16:07,280
师妹
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Please don't

687
01:16:08,190 --> 01:16:08,920
拿开你的脏手
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't touch me

688
01:16:09,530 --> 01:16:11,460
我求求你别告诉师娘
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Please don't tell Simo

689
01:16:11,730 --> 01:16:12,460
我要
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll tell her.

690
01:16:12,900 --> 01:16:14,760
师妹
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't

691
01:16:16,170 --> 01:16:19,460
你为什么要做那些见不得人的事 为什么
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why did you get involved in illegal activities?

692
01:16:20,300 --> 01:16:21,230
为什么
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why did you do it?

693
01:16:25,670 --> 01:16:26,700
我为了师娘
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I did it for Simo

694
01:16:29,330 --> 01:16:31,670
我只要那些药丸治好师娘的病
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I need their medicine for Simo's illness

695
01:16:33,940 --> 01:16:38,100
我只要师娘颐养天年 不再受疼痛之苦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If it stops Simo having to go through any pain

696
01:16:39,180 --> 01:16:40,480
我什么事都肯做
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm willing to do anything

697
01:16:41,450 --> 01:16:43,110
哪怕是不仁不义的事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Even if it's unethical

698
01:16:44,820 --> 01:16:46,280
我从小没爹没娘
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I lost my parents when I was a kid

699
01:16:47,320 --> 01:16:49,050
全靠师娘抚养我长大
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's Simo who took care of me

700
01:16:49,960 --> 01:16:51,790
全靠师父教养我成人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}It's Sifu who taught me the ways of life

701
01:16:52,460 --> 01:16:56,540
我来不及报答师父的恩 也要全心全意报答师娘
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Since I can't repay Sifu, I'll do all I can to repay Simo

702
01:16:57,950 --> 01:17:02,580
梦兰 师娘年事已高 报恩之日无多
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Lan. I don't have much time left to repay Simo

703
01:17:03,290 --> 01:17:04,260
师哥
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Brother

704
01:17:05,960 --> 01:17:07,620
我只为了尽人子之孝
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm at their mercy now

705
01:17:08,460 --> 01:17:12,660
相信我我是不得已 让我替魏家再办一件事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Trust me, I'll do one last thing for the Ngais

706
01:17:14,170 --> 01:17:16,640
再办一件事伤天害理的事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What is it? Something illegal?

707
01:17:18,410 --> 01:17:20,560
你不要多问 我自有分寸
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't ask. I know what I'm doing

708
01:17:21,770 --> 01:17:23,670
过了明天 我们马上回唐山
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We'll return to Tang San the day after tomorrow

709
01:17:40,590 --> 01:17:42,710
魏家的人打来了 快关门
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're here. Close the doors quickly

710
01:17:45,480 --> 01:17:47,180
开门
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Keep the doors open

711
01:17:47,850 --> 01:17:49,320
把门打开
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Open the doors

712
01:17:55,420 --> 01:17:58,720
不准关门 我们百忍道场的人 没有一个是怕死的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't close the doors, we're no cowards.

713
01:17:59,190 --> 01:17:59,920
对 我不怕死
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We're no cowards

714
01:18:00,830 --> 01:18:03,760
魏家人公然找上门来简直目无王法
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Ngais really have no respect for us

715
01:18:06,200 --> 01:18:09,990
爹跟他们讲理也讲不通 我们跟他们拼了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's no point reasoning with them. Let's take them on

716
01:18:11,530 --> 01:18:13,120
师父 他们的人来啦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sifu, they're here

717
01:18:16,030 --> 01:18:17,470
来啦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's go

718
01:18:25,810 --> 01:18:29,650
你们守外面许进不许出 出来一个杀一个
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Guard the area and kill anyone that's not our own

719
01:18:29,950 --> 01:18:30,510
是
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Yes, sir.

720
01:18:31,320 --> 01:18:31,910
大家分开
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Move it

721
01:18:45,390 --> 01:18:49,150
魏苍龙你带这么多人到这里来 到底想怎么样
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ngai, you've brought an army here. What do you want?

722
01:18:50,830 --> 01:18:56,560
姓钟的 你不是叫我兄弟带信来跟我算账吗 我送上门来啦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Chung, didn't you say you wanted to get even with me? Here I am.

723
01:18:57,870 --> 01:19:01,520
你不要这么神气 你平日所作所为你心里有数
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're despicable You should know what wrongs you've done

724
01:19:02,660 --> 01:19:06,890
我当然有数啦 我杀人放火走私贩毒
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Of course Murder, arson. Drugs. I've done them all

725
01:19:07,870 --> 01:19:10,990
你能拿我怎么样 你有证据吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What can you do? Any evidence?

726
01:19:16,540 --> 01:19:19,840
你这种人作恶多端 迟早有报应
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You'll pay for your crimes sooner or later

727
01:19:23,780 --> 01:19:29,470
现在该我跟你算账了 你把许胖子抓了来 人在哪里
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}But now it's your turn to pay for your crime You detained Fatty Hui. Where is he now?

728
01:19:30,180 --> 01:19:31,610
不知道
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't know.

729
01:19:32,050 --> 01:19:32,980
不知道
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You don't know?

730
01:19:34,680 --> 01:19:36,410
我看你是交不出人来啦
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You can't hand him over?

731
01:19:37,320 --> 01:19:39,450
唐浩云 找他要人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tang How Yuen. Go ask him

732
01:19:48,060 --> 01:19:49,990
钟老伯 我先跟你告个罪
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Senior Chung, I apologise in advance

733
01:19:50,560 --> 01:19:52,890
唐浩云 我对你很失望
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tang How Yuen. I'm very disappointed in you

734
01:19:54,330 --> 01:19:57,760
我以为你是一个好汉 怎知道你为虎作伥
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I thought you were a good man I would never have guessed you were a criminal

735
01:20:00,070 --> 01:20:04,000
我受人之禄忠人之事 请你把人交出来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'm only doing my job. Please hand over our man

736
01:20:04,800 --> 01:20:06,860
人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your man?

737
01:20:08,040 --> 01:20:10,370
人是我抓回来的 没那么容易交出来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I arrested your man for a reason. I won't just hand him over

738
01:20:11,240 --> 01:20:16,470
两国交兵各为其主 要是你再不交人我就不客气了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We both have our reasons for this encounter Hand over my man or face the consequences

739
01:20:34,120 --> 01:20:37,490
你真以为你武功好 我们百忍道场的人怕你吗
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do you think you can intimidate us because your Kung Fu's good?

740
01:20:38,190 --> 01:20:40,650
我不想伤和气 只要你们交人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I don't want to resort to violence. Just hand over our man

741
01:20:41,550 --> 01:20:42,540
我们一定不交了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What if we refuse?

742
01:20:43,260 --> 01:20:46,690
你听着 抓了我的人不放 还理直气壮
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've the right to ask for our man back. You shouldn't push your luck

743
01:20:47,560 --> 01:20:49,820
要是你们不放人 魏家就没有错
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The Ngais have the right to ask for their man back

744
01:20:50,060 --> 01:20:51,620
那就算我 错就错到底
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Come and get him, then

745
01:21:18,950 --> 01:21:22,040
老大 你看出来没有 唐浩云手下留情啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Big Bro, have you noticed? Tang How Yuen is being lenient on them

746
01:21:23,950 --> 01:21:25,420
我看我们该下最后一步棋了吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We've got to resort to plan B now.

747
01:21:55,440 --> 01:21:55,920
师父
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sifu.

748
01:21:56,300 --> 01:21:57,530
师父助你一腿
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let me help you

749
01:22:51,230 --> 01:22:52,330
上
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Attack

750
01:23:35,070 --> 01:23:36,580
就用三弹腿打他
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Give it to him

751
01:23:56,080 --> 01:23:57,340
给我上
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. Your turn

752
01:24:26,620 --> 01:24:28,180
小三子 你还不露馅
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sun. Show your true self now

753
01:24:42,470 --> 01:24:43,600
爹
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Dad Dad! Dad!

754
01:24:59,710 --> 01:25:00,540
你伤得怎么样
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Chung, are you OK?

755
01:25:01,180 --> 01:25:03,910
他暗算我
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've been tricked

756
01:25:05,180 --> 01:25:07,670
这是你做梦也想不到的吧
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You'd never have guessed, right?

757
01:25:08,090 --> 01:25:09,520
原来你是魏家的卧底
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}So you're working as an informer for the Ngais

758
01:25:12,320 --> 01:25:15,310
我等了多少年才等到今天
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've waited a few years for this day

759
01:25:16,430 --> 01:25:20,820
我一直待你不错 你这狼心狗肺的东西
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I've treated you very well. You're no better than an animal

760
01:25:21,620 --> 01:25:25,350
你骂我有什么用 只能怪你自己有眼无珠
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There's no use scolding me now. Blame yourself for being so naive

761
01:25:26,430 --> 01:25:30,490
我只有杀了你 才能报魏大爷对我的救命之恩
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}The only way I can repay Ngai for saving me, is with your life

762
01:25:31,700 --> 01:25:35,970
老实告诉你 小喜子是我故意引出去害死的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}To be honest, Kiddo's death was part of my plan too

763
01:25:40,440 --> 01:25:41,660
你为什么要赖在我身上
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Why did you make me the scapegoat?

764
01:25:43,640 --> 01:25:46,870
我要造成你们的误会 加深你们的仇恨
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I wanted to make your misunderstanding with Chung even worse

765
01:25:47,510 --> 01:25:50,070
你有冤洗不清 你才会为魏大爷卖命啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}so you'd work for the Ngais more diligently

766
01:25:50,980 --> 01:25:54,500
对了 这都是我的奇谋妙计啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That's right, we planned all this right from the start

767
01:25:55,680 --> 01:25:59,280
我再告诉你 许胖子还是我叫小三子抓去
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll tell you something, it's me who asked Sun to capture Fatty Hui

768
01:25:59,680 --> 01:26:01,150
再把他杀死灭口
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We killed him too

769
01:26:01,950 --> 01:26:04,150
他是你们魏家的人 为什么要这么做
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}He's the Ngai's man too. Why did you kill him?

770
01:26:04,960 --> 01:26:07,110
牺牲几个人算得了什么呢
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Sacrificing a life is nothing to us

771
01:26:08,450 --> 01:26:13,010
许胖子死在百忍道场 才使我们师出有名啊
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Because Fatty Hui died in Patience Clan's custody we can hold them to account.

772
01:26:13,460 --> 01:26:14,350
唐浩云
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Tang How Yuen

773
01:26:14,590 --> 01:26:15,720
现在只剩三个人
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}There are three of them left,

774
01:26:15,920 --> 01:26:19,360
你把他们打死 百忍道场就没有了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}kill them and Patience Clan will cease to exist

775
01:26:20,060 --> 01:26:22,050
那么你的任务也完了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Your responsibility will also end here

776
01:26:28,070 --> 01:26:32,000
你们这帮人真下流无耻 唐浩云不为你用
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You're despicable I won't be exploited by you

777
01:26:33,770 --> 01:26:35,260
你忘了我们昨天 是怎么讲定的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't forget what we agreed yesterday

778
01:26:36,300 --> 01:26:40,000
你不讲信用 你不想回唐山了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you don't keep your promise, you'll never get back to Tang San

779
01:26:40,670 --> 01:26:42,540
对畜生没有信用这两个字
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What does an animal like you know about promises?

780
01:26:43,310 --> 01:26:44,400
你不听我的命令
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You know what

781
01:26:46,080 --> 01:26:47,570
你该知道我怎么对付你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I'll do if you don't do what I say

782
01:26:50,800 --> 01:26:53,630
你们想怎么对付我 不怕死的上来
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What can you do? Is anyone brave enough to take me on now?

783
01:26:56,540 --> 01:26:58,590
我告诉你们 有我唐浩云在
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}With me here,

784
01:26:59,160 --> 01:27:00,360
谁都不准动姓钟的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}no one shall touch Senior Chung

785
01:27:03,800 --> 01:27:09,100
小唐啊 你别以为你了不起 你是常山赵子龙打不死…
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Young man. Don't be so arrogant You think you're invincible?

786
01:27:22,540 --> 01:27:23,640
真他妈的
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}What the...?

787
01:27:28,680 --> 01:27:29,810
住手
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Look

788
01:27:36,060 --> 01:27:38,530
魏苍龙 你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ngai Chong Loong!

789
01:27:39,590 --> 01:27:43,120
现在两个人在我手里 你要考虑清楚
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}They're both in my hands Act carefully

790
01:27:45,330 --> 01:27:49,090
我老实告诉你 你师娘根本没有病 是我下了毒
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}To be honest, your Simo wasn't ill I poisoned her

791
01:27:50,330 --> 01:27:55,360
你把他们三个人打死 我就给你解药 放你回唐山
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Kill the three of them and I'll give you the antidote

792
01:27:56,970 --> 01:27:58,300
我们的事一了百了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}We'll call it quits when you're back in Tang San

793
01:27:58,740 --> 01:28:03,470
这也是我的锦囊妙计 是我派小三子去下的毒
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}That was one of my great ideas too I had Sun lace the tea with poison

794
01:28:03,840 --> 01:28:05,640
你要是不听我大哥的命令
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If you don't do what Big Bro says

795
01:28:06,850 --> 01:28:12,640
你师娘非疼死不可 我看你还是听话的好
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}your Simo will die a painful death Just be obedient

796
01:28:13,840 --> 01:28:16,680
你要是不听我的话 只要我一举手
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Don't think about it for long. I just need to give the sign

797
01:28:18,350 --> 01:28:19,900
这两条命就没有了
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}and it'll be the end of them

798
01:28:20,980 --> 01:28:26,280
浩云 你怎么一直瞒着我 你怎么会跟这种坏人做事
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. Why did you keep this from me? Why did you work for these people?

799
01:28:27,860 --> 01:28:29,880
我 我…
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}I...

800
01:28:31,130 --> 01:28:33,120
姓魏的 你不要逼他
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Ngai Chong Loong, there's no point forcing him

801
01:28:34,100 --> 01:28:36,820
浩云 你师父一生忠义
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}How Yuen. Your Sifu was a righteous man

802
01:28:37,270 --> 01:28:40,280
假如你帮人为非作歹 他会死不瞑目
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}If he knew what you were doing now, he'd turn in his grave

803
01:28:40,960 --> 01:28:46,990
不要管我 为了唐山门的名誉着想 好好的照顾师妹
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Do it for me and for the good name of Tang San Clan Take good care of your Lan

804
01:28:48,130 --> 01:28:49,830
妈
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Mum, Mum!

805
01:29:00,880 --> 01:29:02,270
师娘
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Simo!

806
01:29:58,910 --> 01:30:02,000
你这个畜生 我打死你
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}You, animal! Die!

807
01:32:06,050 --> 01:32:07,180
接住
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Die!

808
01:36:00,660 --> 01:36:01,990
走 走
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Let's go.  Let's go

809
01:36:07,520 --> 01:36:08,630
师哥
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}Brother

810
01:36:34,990 --> 01:36:36,960
师娘 妈
{\fnTahoma}{\fs14}{\c&H00FFFF&}{\3c&H000000&}- Simo! - Mum!

